{"tid":1794037,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"和你捐","createTime":"2019-12-22T23:45:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-23T00:26:16.000Z","uid":269159,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"365dbad84074e0a20a83c4115b3fcc4550c1f3f0","tid":1794037,"uid":269159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T23:45:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">11月小妹post過，而家唔夠血喇 重post!</span><br />\n<br />\n為咗展現高質民意反極權，而遊行/集會/以武制暴 只係展現民意其中抗爭方式<br />\n<br />\n有人話抗爭要融入生活，呢類運動正好食正個理念<br />\n<br />\n與其我地有咁多人 不如一齊做善事 比全世界人知道 「我們不是暴徒，而係充滿愛心，愛香港既香港人」<br />\n因此我有一個建議：<br />\n<br />\n一齊去做有意義 亦對社會有實質貢獻工作<br />\n例如 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />全民捐血<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前成日聽到血庫唔夠血 要 呼籲捐血<br />\n不如就一齊去啦，因為多區都有捐血站，個行為等於開花，不過係善事開花，相信能夠<br />\n正面地展現抗爭可愛一面<br />\n<br />\n一日捐唔晒 就下星期再捐，捐到血庫爆為止！<br />\n<br />\n唯一係安全考慮，因為要登記ID先可以捐血，所以全日係以和理非姿態進行，當然可以加文宣配合以免比狗咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果覺得可以請幫推同埋研究文宣同set日程，sorry因為我唔識搞文宣呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n參考各區捐血站<br />\n<a href=\"https://www5.ha.org.hk/rcbts/hkarticle.asp?bid=85&amp;MenuID=5#.Xc9TfyV-WaM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww5.ha.org.hk%2Frcbts%2Fhkarticle.asp%3Fbid%3D85%26MenuID%3D5%23.Xc9TfyV-WaM&d=HJ1jiXHXfxJ2%2FxolOfbUwc70t8psI8cu6Rjg0MoA49o%3D&h=521374ca\" target=\"_blank\">https://www5.ha.org.hk/rcbts/hkarticle.asp?bid=85&amp;MenuID=5#.Xc9TfyV-WaM</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qeHqY4s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqeHqY4s.jpg&h=2cc269b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n搞個暗黑全民日笑下：<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />全民捐精日<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d20f66336f1af86a1624d50cdd0f7879ae63cb9","tid":1794037,"uid":27349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T23:56:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6aa552339959dc933b0b477ac3cae3319a93a317","tid":1794037,"uid":269159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d20f66336f1af86a1624d50cdd0f7879ae63cb9","tid":1794037,"uid":27349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T23:56:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T00:26:16.000Z","msg":"真係唔知係支那"}]}